dataObject.content: As dear leader Mitch McConnell (R-Ky.) is fond of saying, "winners make policy, losers go home." And yet unfortunately, Republicans in the Senate refuse to take the phrase to heart. Which is a real shame. We are just under 280 days into the Trump presidency, yet beyond nominations, Congress has made almost no progress passing the agenda America elected them to enact.
